abstract: In this talk, I’ll share the journey of building an AI-powered virtual assistant for literature reviews, developed for a European agency.
Using LlamaIndex, OpenAI, Claude+, and other models, the tool helps researchers quickly synthesize insights.
It’s been applied to assess AI’s labor market impact, redefining research efficiency.
